The paper focuses on using deep learning models for medical imaging analysis, specifically for computer-aided diagnosis of ocular diseases using funduscopic images. This falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with medical applications (cs.MED) and information retrieval (cs.IR) in terms of diagnosing diseases from images.
